text: Young America is a 1932 American drama movie directed by Frank Borzage and starring Spencer Tracy, Doris Kenyon, Ralph Bellamy, Beryl Mercer, Sarah Padden. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * Category:1932 drama movies Category:1930s American drama movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Frank Borzage
